OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FThe UK's Eurovision entry Look Mum No
OL,8,FComputer has finished last in the song
OL,9,Fcontest's 2026 grand final with just
OL,10,Fone point, as Bulgaria celebrated the
OL,11,Fcountry's first ever win.
OL,13,FIt is the fourth consecutive year in a
OL,14,Frow that the UK has received no points
OL,15,Ffrom the public vote, with the
OL,16,Fcountry's only jury point coming from
OL,17,FUkraine, while Bulgaria's Dara scored
OL,18,F516 points with Bangaranga.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
