FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FIt comes after Lincolnshire-born Look
OL,8,FMum No Computer, whose real name is
OL,9,FSam Battle, performed his song Eins,
OL,10,FZwei, Drei at the Wiener Stadthalle in
OL,11,FVienna, Austria, while dancing
OL,12,Fenergetically with people dressed as
OL,13,Fcomputers on Saturday night.
OL,15,FBulgaria secured victory after a tense
OL,16,Ffinale in the contest's 70th year,
OL,17,Fwhich saw Israel in first place until
OL,18,Fthe last points were announced,
OL,19,Feventually finishing second with 343
OL,20,Fpoints.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FIsrael's participation in Eurovision
OL,8,Fthis year led to a boycott from
OL,9,FIreland, Iceland, the Netherlands,
OL,10,FSpain and Slovenia, due to its actions
OL,11,Fin Gaza.
OL,13,FIsraeli entrant Noam Bettan, 28, sang
OL,14,Fhis song Michelle, in English, Hebrew
OL,15,Fand French, while some chants and
OL,16,Fbooing could be heard in the crowd,
OL,17,Fwhere many Israel flags and banners
OL,18,Fcould also be seen.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FRomania's Alexandra Capitanescu, with
OL,8,Fthe intense pop metal song Choke Me,
OL,9,Ffinished third on 296 points.
OL,11,FBattle's performance saw him attempt
OL,12,Fto get the crowd to sing with him,
OL,13,Fchanting: "When I say eins, you say
OL,14,Fzwei."
OL,16,FThe YouTube star wore a pink boiler
OL,17,Fsuit as performers in fluffy headwear
OL,18,Fdanced in a mock workshop, while he
OL,19,Fplayed a synthesiser, and ended up in
OL,20,Fa cardboard box.
OL,26,@uD@KOUvD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
