OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FIn a Facebook post after the
OL,8,Fcompetition, Battle said Dara was the
OL,9,F"honestly deserved winner".
OL,11,F"Met a lot of amazing folk," the post
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"The most important thing is we all
OL,15,Ftried our hardest. Regardless of what
OL,16,Fis against us. Whatever it may be.
OL,17,FGotta keep trying your hardest
OL,18,Fregardless of the foooookennnn
OL,19,Foutcome!!!"
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@ZO]sD@AOUsD@\O]vD@AOU{D@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
