OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FHe follows Remember Monday, Olly
OL,8,FAlexander and Mae Muller in receiving
OL,9,Fno points from the public vote.
OL,11,FThe UK gave its 12 points to France in
OL,12,Fthe jury vote, which was presented by
OL,13,Fdrag artist La Voix and also saw
OL,14,FBulgaria awarded 10 points, Czechia
OL,15,Fawarded eight and Ukraine given seven.
OL,17,FElsewhere, Daniel Zizka, the act from
OL,18,Fthe Czech Republic, appeared to be
OL,19,Fplagued by technical difficulties
OL,20,Fduring his performance of the song
OL,21,FCrossroads.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
