PN,30209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FShe sang her song Jalla, wearing a
OL,8,Fwhite bralette and dress, as hands
OL,9,Freached up from the stage below her,
OL,10,Fwhile flames shot out from behind her
OL,11,Fand her backing dancers waved towels.
OL,13,FMidway through her performance,
OL,14,FAntigoni turned to the audience and
OL,15,Ftold them: "You want more."
OL,17,FAt the end of her performance, she
OL,18,Fadded: "Thank you, Europe."
OL,26,@wD@LOUwD@[O]zD@HOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/15
