OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FAustralian pop star Delta Goodrem also
OL,8,Fperformed her song Eclipse, with which
OL,9,Fshe is representing her home country,
OL,10,Fat the grand final of the Eurovision
OL,11,FSong Contest.
OL,13,FThe 41-year-old was accompanied by a
OL,14,Fharpist before eventually miming
OL,15,Fplaying a gold sparkly piano herself.
OL,17,FAs the former Neighbours star's
OL,18,Fperformance climaxed she was elevated
OL,19,Finto the air from the top of the
OL,20,Fpiano, as fireworks went off around
OL,21,Fher.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
