PN,30211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FGreece's Akylas attracted attention on
OL,8,Fsocial media with his video game-
OL,9,Finspired performance of his song Ferto.
OL,11,FThe Greek delegation has been handing
OL,12,Fout replicas of the singer's hat to
OL,13,Ffans and media during the week, with
OL,14,FAkylas being among the best supported
OL,15,Facts in Vienna.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
