FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FOne eccentric performance came from
OL,8,FLithuania's Lion Ceccah, who gave an
OL,9,Feye-catching performance with his head
OL,10,Fand hands painted silver, wearing a
OL,11,Fblack sculpture-like costume at the
OL,12,Fstart of his performance.
OL,14,FThe final comes after Israel's Bettan
OL,15,Fwas booed by the crowd during his
OL,16,Fperformance in Tuesday's semi-final,
OL,17,Freceiving a mixed reception before his
OL,18,Fperformance began, with some members
OL,19,Fof the audience shouting and later
OL,20,Fbooing, during the quiet moments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FThere were a number of protests in the
OL,8,FAustrian capital this week over
OL,9,FIsrael's inclusion in the contest amid
OL,10,Fits actions in Gaza.
OL,12,FThe largest protest was the No Stage
OL,13,FFor Genocide event, organised by
OL,14,FPalestine Solidarity Austria, which
OL,15,Ftook place at Venediger Au, a playpark
OL,16,Fon the outskirts of Vienna, which was
OL,17,Fattended by hundreds of supporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30214
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FThere was also a march from the city's
OL,8,Fwestern train station to the area
OL,9,Fwhere the Wiener Stadthalle is located
OL,10,Fon Saturday, but police directed
OL,11,Fprotesters away from the venue in a
OL,12,Floop.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,303,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30215
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F302A1778983452
OL,3,CUK's Look Mum No Computer last in
OL,4,CEurovision final as Bulgaria wins
OL,5,Cfirst trophy
OL,7,FEarlier this week, human rights group
OL,8,FAmnesty International criticised the
OL,9,FEuropean Broadcasting Union for its
OL,10,Ffailure to suspend Israel from the
OL,11,Fsong contest, as it did with Russia
OL,12,Fafter its full-scale invasion of
OL,13,FUkraine in 2022, calling it an act of
OL,14,F"cowardice" and a "blatant double
OL,15,Fstandard".
